The step of Crisp-dm are
1. Business Understanding -> identify the business problem, understand how we can solve it
2. Data Understanding -> analyze available data sources. 
3. Data Preparation -> transform the data o it can be put into a ML algorithm
4. Modelling -> Training the models, select the best one model
5. Evaluation -> measure how well the model solves the business problem
6. Deployment -> deploy the model to production section
Iterate this step!
